<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Couple’s Shower | FIORE</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <!-- AOS Library CDN -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="couples-shower">

  <!-- AOS Library JS -->
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.js"></script>
  <script>
    AOS.init({
      duration: 2500,  // Animation lasts for 2500 milliseconds
      delay: 300,      // Delay animation by 300 milliseconds before it starts
      once: true       // Ensures animations run only once (when scrolling down) 
    });
  </script>

  <section class="hero-section couple-hero">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1>Couple’s Shower</h1>
      <p>Celebrate Love, Together</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="intro-section" data-aos="fade-up">
    <p>
        The Couple’s Shower is a sophisticated and joyful gathering that honors the love story of both the bride and groom. It's a unique opportunity for close friends and family to come together in celebration, showering the couple with affection, thoughtful gifts, and well wishes. Set in an atmosphere of laughter, elegance, and heartfelt connection, this event beautifully blends tradition with modern charm. From curated games and gourmet treats to sentimental toasts and shared memories, every moment is designed to reflect the couple’s journey and build anticipation for the wedding day ahead. It’s where love, luxury, and lasting memories intertwine in perfect harmony.
    </p>
  </section>
  
  

  <main class="couple-wrapper">

    <section class="split-section" data-aos="zoom-in">
      <img src="/img/cs-img.jpg" alt="His & Hers Lounge">
      <div class="text-content">
        <h2>His & Hers Lounge Areas</h2>
        <p>Create tailored comfort zones for both sides—cocktail bar for him, mimosa bar for her—complete with cozy seating and signature scents.</p>
        <a href="/decorators" class="luxury-button">Design Your Space</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="split-section reverse" data-aos="zoom-in">
      <img src="/img/cs-img3.jpg" alt="Couple Story Wall">
      <div class="text-content">
        <h2>‘Our Story’ Wall</h2>
        <p>Celebrate your love journey with a photo timeline, pinned letters, and shared favorite moments—framed beautifully for guests to explore.</p>
        
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="split-section" data-aos="zoom-in">
      <img src="/img/cs-drinks.png" alt="Custom Cocktail Bar">
      <div class="text-content">
        <h2>Custom Cocktail & Mocktail Bar</h2>
        <p>Create ‘His & Hers’ signature drinks with fun names, elegant glassware, and matching colors. Add recipe cards for guests to take home!</p>
        
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="split-section reverse" data-aos="zoom-in">
      <img src="/img/cs-game2.png" alt="Co-ed Games">
      <div class="text-content">
        <h2>Co-ed Game Time</h2>
        <p>Interactive games like Couple Trivia, Memory Match, and “How Well Do You Know Them?” bring guests from both sides together in fun.</p>
        <a href="/Couple_shower_games" class="luxury-button">Plan Fun Moments</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="split-section" data-aos="zoom-in">
      <img src="/img/cs-gift2.png" alt="Joint Gift Registry">
      <div class="text-content">
        <h2>Joint Gift Registry Station</h2>
        <p>Let guests browse a curated gift list using QR codes, or leave advice cards and well-wishes for the couple in personalized message boxes.</p>
       
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="split-section reverse" data-aos="zoom-in">
      <img src="/img/cs-last.png" alt="Photo & Chill Lounge">
      <div class="text-content">
        <h2>Photo Lounge & Keepsake Book</h2>
        <p>Capture every smile in a chic photo lounge. Each snapshot goes into a keepsake scrapbook signed by guests—a lasting memory of the day.</p>
        <a href="/photographer_collection" class="luxury-button">Book a Photographer</a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

</body>
</html>
